name: The Buidlers and Hodlers
description:
The Buidlers and Hodlers is a riff on the famous Diggers and Dealers mining forum that happens every year in Kalgoorlie.

The purpose of these two days is to meet other crypto people, swap ideas and stories and to help spread the word about this emerging asset class to Western Australian regional communities.


This NFT token can be claimed by the people who attended the first Builders and Hodlers meetup in Toodyay, Western Australia on the 27th of November 2021.
